  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A varied breakfast buffet is available each morning with hot and cold options as well as freshly-brewed coffees, teas and locally-sourced fruit juices. Breakfast is served each day in the first floor panoramic breakfast room. Dinner is served up here too. You'll have a three course meal each evening, with choices.</p>
<p><strong>Bistro Restaurant </strong>has panoramic floor-to-ceiling windows with views of the harbour. Choose <span>from tasty appetisers, meat, fish, pastas and risotto dishes all prepared with the freshest of ingredients. </span></p>
<p><strong>The Lounge Bar </strong>sprawls out onto the lake front terrace and is well known for its cocktail list and wine selection. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
