  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Europa is in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a> with unrivalled views of the harbour. This classic hotel is a comfortable base to come back to after a day of sightseeing and exploring the local area.</p>
<h2>Lake views for everyone</h2>
<p>Enjoy them from the restaurant's floor-to-ceiling windows - the chefs here pride themselves on their use of local ingredients. We love the fish platters and antipasti that come fresh from the market. The hotel's rooftop is the place to be; chill out in the small heated pool and relax on sun terrace with great views over the lake and mountains.</p>
<h2>Great base for exploring</h2>
<p>Riva itself is a spectacular town to explore. It's got a lot to offer - like water sports, mountain hiking and some great biking trails. Exploring other resorts on the lake is also easy with the ferry port just a few steps away from the hotel.</p>]]></description>
