  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>are small and comfortable at about 14-18m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They're located at the back of the hotel.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are about 15-19m² and sleep up to two people. They have lovely lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are about 10m² and are a great choice for solo travellers. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning (from mid-June to mid-September)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Mini-fridge</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. <span>€</span>8 per day, payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
